{"type":null,"faqId":49532,"title":"更改声音设置","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"声音设置\"XE \"铃声设置\"XE \"声音\"XE \"铃声\"XE \"音量\"XE \"静音\"XE \"振动\"XE \"更改铃声\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189878\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“声音”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>在“声音”界面，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“音量”，调整音乐、来电、通知、闹钟或通话等的音量大小。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“静音模式”开关，开启或关闭静音模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“静音时振动”开关，开启或关闭手机静音时的振动效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“卡 1 响铃时振动”或“卡 2 响铃时振动”开关，开启或关闭手机来电响铃时的振动效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“卡 1 来电铃声”或“卡 2 来电铃声”，设置卡 1 和卡 2 来电铃声。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“默认通知铃声”，设置通知铃声。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“系统”区域下的开关，开启或关闭手机的触摸、锁屏、拨号键盘等的提示音或振动效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>后续处理</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189879\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>此界面上的选项可能与手机实际显示有差异，请以手机实际显示为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5276","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294504000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":141,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}